The paper deals with a communication system (broadcast channel) with imperfect and unmatched channel state information, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and communication systems (cs.COMM). The use of subchannels and sub-optimal schemes also relates to networked systems (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). The study of the Degrees-of-Freedom (DoF) region is also relevant to control systems (cs.SY).
